%F A269940 T(n,k) = (-1)^k*FF(n+k,n)*P[n,k](n/(n+1)) where P is the P-transform and FF the falling factorial function. For the definition of the P-transform see the link.
%F A269940 T(n,k) = A268438(n,k)*FF(n+k,n)/(2*n)!.
